author: Al Jazeera
title: Sweden's liberal virus strategy questioned as death toll mounts
description: While large gatherings have been banned, Sweden has yet to enforce movement restrictions seen in other European nations.
content:
A spike in novel coronavirus infections and deaths in Stockholm has raised questions about Sweden's decision to fight the outbreak without resorting to the lockdowns that have left much of Europe at a standstill.
